    "content": "<h4 id=\"unconscious\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; margin-bottom: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Russo One', sans-serif; font-size: 0.35cm; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: #c40f0f; background-repeat: no-repeat; text-transform: uppercase;\">UNCONSCIOUS</h4>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 24px; color: #1c1c1c; font-family: 'Open Sans'; font-size: 13px; background-repeat: no-repeat;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">An unconscious creature is incapacitated (see the condition), can&rsquo;t move or speak, and is unaware of its surroundings</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">The creature drops whatever it&rsquo;s holding and falls prone.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">The creature automatically fails Strength and Dexterity saving throws.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Attack rolls against the creature have advantage.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; user-select: text; background-repeat: no-repeat; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Any attack that hits the creature is a critical hit if the attacker is within 5 feet of the creature.</li>\n</ul>",
